title: VivoCity SG

creator: VivoCity Singapore
descriptionHtml:
The VivoCity SG App is a one-stop platform for you to enjoy a seamless shopping experience at VivoCity.

Download the app and sign up for VivoRewards+, the shopper loyalty programme that allows you to convert your purchases into rewards you love!

Get the best out of your shopping experience whether you are in-mall or at home, using the in-app features that will help you plan your shopping trip!

Favourite App Feature Include:
• Browse mall and store information
• Discover retailers and restaurants
• Search for products
• Find exclusive deals and events
• Maintain a list of favourite store and events
• Stay informed on the latest happening and promotions in the mall
• Share information with friends or send an event to your phone calendar
• Sign up for VivoRewards+ and earn VRPoints with your purchases
• Use VRPoints to redeem rewards of your choice from the Rewards Catalogue
• Sign up and submit receipts to unlock Kids Club Super Buddy benefits
• Get real-time updates on carpark availability in the mall
descriptionShort: A brand-new shopping experience awaits you on VivoCity SG App.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
VivoRewards is now VivoRewards+! The shopper loyalty programme that allows you to convert your purchases into rewards you love. Earn VRPoints when you shop and dine at VivoCity and use them to exchange for rewards and perks including shopping & dining vouchers, Parking$, Mapletree Vouchers and more!

Latest Features:
- Revamped user interface
- Rewards Catalogue
- Periodic Flash Deals
- eVoucher download
- In-App eWallet

title: VivoCity SG

creator: VivoCity Singapore
descriptionHtml:
Get the most out of your visit to VivoCity with the VivoCity SG app!
Become a VivoRewards+ member to get fantastic rewards when you shop and dine at VivoCity. Get access to the latest updates about parking availability, store information and be notified on the latest promotions and offers available. Enrol the little ones in our Kids Club program for invitations to fun, exciting events and make use of exclusive member offers and discounts at participating outlets.

Earn VRPoints As You Shop
Members can earn VRPoints with every successful transaction made at participating outlets.
Accumulate VRPoints to redeem exciting rewards in-app, including Flash Deals, eVouchers, Parking$, Mapletree Vouchers and more!
Personalized unique member QR Code
Submit receipts using in-app scanner
Multiply your VRPoints by linking up your VivoRewards+ account with DBS
Track your VRPoints, upcoming expiry of points, available parking$ at a glance
See your transaction records under “Activity”
*Please refer to the program terms and conditions for more details.

REWARDS CATALOGUE
Browse through Rewards listings in our catalogue and redeem your favourite using VRPoints.
Select from Store Deals, Parking$ and VivoCity Specials
Turn on app notifications to be informed on periodic Flash Deals listings
Sort by category or store name for easy navigation

PERSONAL eWallet
Manage your rewards and eVouchers with ease using our eWallet feature.
eVouchers redeemed in-app will be stored in the eWallet
Review all available eVouchers at a glance
Track your eVoucher usage and expiry dates

VivoCity Kids Club
Because everyone should be treated special at VivoCity regardless of age, enrol the kids in VivoCity’s Kids Club
and discover perks and offerings that will delight their little hearts.
Free Membership for children aged 3 – 12 years old
Accumulate spend to achieve Super Buddy status
Birthday surprises, exclusive perks and priority invitations to Kids Clubs events.
Offers and discounts at participating stores
descriptionShort: A brand-new shopping experience awaits you on VivoCity SG App.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What’s New:
Features & reliability enhancements
Bug Fixes
Update of VivoRewards User Agreement

Get access to the latest updates about parking availability, store information and be notified on the latest promotions and offers available. Enrol the little ones in our Kids Club program for invitations to fun, exciting events and make use of exclusive member offers and discounts at participating outlets.

Earn VRPoints As You Shop
Members can earn VRPoints with every successful transaction made at participating outlets.
Accumulate VRPoints to redeem exciting rewards in-app, including Flash Deals, eVouchers, Parking$, Mapletree Vouchers and more!
Personalized unique member QR Code
Submit receipts using in-app scanner
Multiply your VRPoints by linking up your VivoRewards+ account with DBS
Track your VRPoints, upcoming expiry of points, available parking$ at a glance
See your transaction records under “Activity”
*Please refer to the program terms and conditions for more details.

REWARDS CATALOGUE
Browse through Rewards listings in our catalogue and redeem your favourite using VRPoints.
Select from Store Deals, Parking$ and VivoCity Specials
Turn on app notifications to be informed on periodic Flash Deals listings
Sort by category or store name for easy navigation

PERSONAL eWallet
Manage your rewards and eVouchers with ease using our eWallet feature.
eVouchers redeemed in-app will be stored in the eWallet
Review all available eVouchers at a glance
Track your eVoucher usage and expiry dates

VivoCity Kids Club
Because everyone should be treated special at VivoCity regardless of age, enrol the kids in VivoCity’s Kids Club
and discover perks and offerings that will delight their little hearts.
Free Membership for children aged 3 – 12 years old
Accumulate spend to achieve Super Buddy status
Birthday surprises, exclusive perks and priority invitations to Kids Clubs events.
Offers and discounts at participating stores
